<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1948-09-24T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-05-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="355" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d355">
                                <head><hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi></head>
                                <p>This meeting is listed in the Log, <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>,
                                        <ref target="#pg_461">p. 461</ref>, but no record of the
                                    conversation has been found. The visit of the Soviet Chargé
                                    d’Affaires lasted at most twenty minutes and was presumably in
                                    the nature of a courtesy call.</p>
                            </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>